People are searching for the audio book, "Intentions from the Heart" - which I placed as first result. The other 2 results are simply material on the topic, "intention."

People are searching for the book, "Attaining the Worlds Beyond." 1st result - eBook (PDF if possible). 2nd result - audio book. After that, material related to the book (3 - promo clip, 4 - lessons etc.). Since there is organizational goal to sell books, then there should be integration of bookstore into kabbalahmedia.info, either as ad-like search results (similar to Google Ads appearing first in Google search results), which links to external site selling the books, or as side banner with photo of book being searched, and options to directly buy (1) the physical copy of the book, (2) eBook, (3) audio book.
